Package minesweeper.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    Contains information about game cells and has basic methods to change it's status.
    FileContainer
    This class handles the creation and initialization of the image and text files used by the program
    Minefield
    Contains the Information about the minefield and contains all the cells of the game.
    Score
    Stores Score Information
    ScoreKeeper
    This object holds the current scores in TreeMaps and is used to check if the completion times are good enough to be recorded.
    ScoreSaver
    This class is used to write scores into the .txt files
